  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a hot pot vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the mustard seeds and cumin seeds and cook until they start to splutter.",
    "Add the couscous and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the water and salt, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the condensed milk and cook for another 2 minutes.",
    "Serve hot in the hot pot vessel."
